{"id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0002", "text": "Digital transformation offers opportunities for logistics companies, but at the same time increases the vulnerability of the chain. One in five companies is now affected by a cyber attack. The use of AI also makes cyber attacks more dangerous. During a webinar, experts discuss the increase in cyber risks in the Transport & Logistics sector.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0002", "source_slug": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen", "source_title": "From cyber risks to solutions", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen.html", "source_date": "2025-05-27", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0003", "text": "Under the leadership of moderator Rieneke Kok, Richard Verbrugge - cybersecurity expert at ABN AMRO - and Marijn van Schoote - managing director at FERM and CISO at Port of Rotterdam - discuss cyber threats and the impact of the NIS2 legislation.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0003", "source_slug": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen", "source_title": "From cyber risks to solutions", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen.html", "source_date": "2025-05-27", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "Frank Maaskant, Warehouse Manager at Windhorst Transport, will also speak. Frank shares how the company ensures cybersecurity.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen", "source_title": "From cyber risks to solutions", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen.html", "source_date": "2025-05-27", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "- The most important cybersecurity risks for logistics companies in 2025\n- The impact of the NIS2 directive on the sector\n- How to deal with cyber incidents and what response strategies are necessary\n- Practical insights and best practices", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen", "source_title": "From cyber risks to solutions", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen.html", "source_date": "2025-05-27", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
