{"id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0009", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0009", "source_slug": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen", "source_title": "From cyber risks to solutions", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen.html", "source_date": "2025-05-27", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0010", "text": "- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) and reduce your cyber risks.\n- View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars on our [Safe entrepreneurship page](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link).\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen__c4-paragraph__0010", "source_slug": "van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen", "source_title": "From cyber risks to solutions", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/van-cyberrisicos-naar-oplossingen.html", "source_date": "2025-05-27", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
